high_descs: Move forward to the right side of the tall white dresser.
Open the bottom right drawer of the dresser and pick up the tissue box in there.
Bring the tissue box to the lamp on the left side of the dresser.
Turn on the lamp on the dresser.

high_descs: Move slightly right and proceed to dresser.
Open bottom right drawer of dresser, remove box of tissues, and close drawer.
Turn left, proceed to wall.  Turn right, proceed to dresser.
Turn on lamp on top of dresser.
anns.task_desc: Get box of tissues out of drawer and turn on lamp.

high_descs: Move to the right side of the large dresser facing the shelf on the bottom right

Carry the tissue box to the top left of the white dresser facing the lamp on top
